#

Grilled New York Strip Steak with Garlic Herb Butter

$25.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 50%

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

SteakGrilledGourmetAmerican

Description

Juicy New York strip steak grilled to perfection, topped with a rich garlic herb butter for a savory finish.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 2 (8 oz)
  • Unsalted Butter: 1/2 cup
  • Garlic: 4 cloves
  • Fresh Parsley: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh Thyme: 1 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
